Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅魂一共還剩多少隻？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟還有像白亞那樣的分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經抓了半數以上了
